Package com.weapons

Class FireBulletWeapon

java.lang.Object
com.weapons.Weapon
com.weapons.FireBulletWeapon
All Implemented Interfaces:
WeaponInterface
public class FireBulletWeapon
extends Weapon
implements WeaponInterface
FireBulletWeapon class set bullet goes in same direction as weapons bullet travels fast and is small (you pick speed, size) bullet must collide exactly with other vehicles, to reduce their health by 10%
